 ftp://192.168.1.2/

1. install sublime Text
(1) 安装
下载地址：http://www.sublimetext.com/2
tar -zxvf Sublime Text 2.0.2 x64.tar.bz2
mv Sublime\ Text\ 2 /usr/lib/
ln -s /usr/lib/Sublime\ Text\ 2/sublime_text /usr/bin/sublime
(2) 中文输入
sudo apt-get install xfonts-wqy
cd ~/.config/sublime-text-2/Packages
git clone https://github.com/xgenvn/InputHelper.git
(3) 参考文档 : http://jingyan.baidu.com/article/3aed632e66dc877011809166.html



2. install git
(1) 安装 : apt-get install git
(2) git init /home/nyf/NYF/develop
(3) git clone https://github.com/niyoufa/nyf.git


3. install nodejs
(1) 安装
下载源码: node-v0.12.3.tar.gz 
解压 : tar -xvf node-v0.12.3.tar.gz
./configure
make
make install 
(2) 部署消息服务器
1.1 进入message_server目录
1.2 npm install 
1.3 安装redis-server : apt-get install redis-server 
1.4 安装protobuf-2.5.0 
./configure
make 
make install 
cd python 
python setup.py build 
python setup.py install 
配置成功！

4. install ubuntu14.04 32 位 chrome
sudo apt-get -f install
wget https://dl.google.com/linux/direct/google-chrome-stable_current_i386.deb
sudo dpkg -i google-chrome-stable_current_i386.deb

5. install pip 
sudo apt-get install python-pip

6. install postgres
http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_6af33caa0100ypck.html
apt-get install -y postgresql-9.3 postgresql-client-9.3 postgresql-contrib-9.3 postgresql-server-dev-9.3
create user nyf with password 'pku123';
alter role nyf with superuser;
create database new_gflux with owner = nyf ;
备份数据库 : pg_dump -U username database_name >  backupfile_name
备份数表 : pg_dump -U username  database_name -t table_name > backupfile_name
还原备份文件到数据库 : 在数据库命令行执行 \i backupfile_path

7. 安装python模块问题
(1) ascii codec can't decode byte 0xe8 in position 0:ordinal not in range(128) 
方法 : 
在出现问题的页加上如下三行即可：
import sys
reload(sys)
sys.setdefaultencoding('utf-8') 

(2) 安装python模块时出现：error: Setup script exited with error: command 'gcc' failed with exit status 1
方法 : sudo apt-get install python-dev xlwt

8. gcustomer加密模块

apt-get install python-m2crypto

9. install easy_install 	
sudo apt-get install python-setuptools

10. easy_install安装MySQL-python
sudo easy_install MySQL-python
报错 : 
EnvironmentError: mysql_config not found
方法 : http://www.cnblogs.com/xiazh/archive/2012/12/12/2814289.html
sudo apt-get install libmysqlclient-dev 
找到mysql_config文件的路径 :  whereis mysql_config
sudo updatedb
locate mysql_config

11. install mysql 

(1) apt-get install 
I. sudo apt-get install mysql-server
 
II. apt-get isntall mysql-client

III.  sudo apt-get install libmysqlclient-dev

查看安装是否成功 : sudo netstat -tap | grep mysql
登录 : mysql -u root -p 

IV 查看deb包 
 dpkg -l | grep mysql 

 V 删除软件包 
 dpkg -r package


(2) dpkg install 


12. install redis 
(1) apt-get install 

apt-get install redis-server 

(2) dpkg install 
sudo dpkg -i redis-server_2%3a2.8.4-2_i386.deb redis-tools_2%3a2.8.4-2_i386.deb


13. 搭建ftp
Ubuntu下搭建FTP服务器
http://blog.csdn.net/njchenyi/article/details/8499555

 530 Login incorrect 解决方法 
 http://blog.chinaunix.net/uid-23381466-id-58767.html

500 OOPS: vsftpd: refusing to run with writable root inside chroot()解决方法 
http://blog.csdn.net/bluishglc/article/details/42399439

227 Entering Passive Mode (127,0,0,1,162,137).
http://m.blog.csdn.net/blog/xznuwdh/6061694

553 Could not create file.
修改ftp目录权限


anon_other_write_enable=YES